OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with outbreaks of rain,
OL,7,Fheavy at times. Then staying cloudy
OL,8,Fovernight with some lighter rain and
OL,9,Fdrizzle, this mostly in the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FMainly cloudy with outbreaks
OL,12,Fof rain, mostly light but occasionally
OL,13,Fheavier northwest. Some brightness
OL,14,Faround the Moray Firth. Becoming
OL,15,Flargely dry in the evening although
OL,16,Fsome drizzle in the northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
